texts.content: {"text":"4. Hech bir jon yo`qki, uning hifz qilib turuvchisi bo`lmasa.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"7. U (suv) sulb (orqa umurtqa) va taroib \n(ko`krak suyagi) orasidan chiqadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,77]}]}

{"text":"10. Bas (o`shanda) u(inson)da quvvat ham, nusrat beruvchi ham bo`lmaydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,73]}]}

{"text":"17. Bas, kofirlarga muhlat ber. \nHa, ularga ozgina muhlat ber.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,62]}]}

{"text":"1. Oliy qadar bo`lgan \nRobbing ismini poklab yod et.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,52]}]}

{"text":"3. U, o`lchov bilan qilgan va \nhidoyatga boshlagan Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,58]}]}

{"text":"6. Biz senga (Qur'onni) qiroat qildiramiz, bas, sen uni esdan chiqarmassan.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"7. Illo, Alloh xohlaganini. Albatta, U oshkorni ham, maxfiy narsalarni ham biladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,83]}]}

{"text":"13. So`ngra, uning ichida o`lmay ham, tirilmay ham qoladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"15. Va Robbi ismini zikr qilsa \n va namoz o`qisa hamdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"8. O`shal kunda bir chehralar ne'mat xursandligi bilan to`ladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"23. Illo, kim yuz o`girsa va kofir bo`lsa...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,44]}]}

{"text":"24. Bas, uni Alloh katta azob bilan azoblaydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"5. Mana shularda aql egasi uchun \n(qanoatlantiruvchi) qasam bordir?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"9. Va vodiyda xarsang toshlarni kesib \n(imorat yasagan) Samudni.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"13. Bas, Robbing ularning boshiga turli azoblarni quydi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"15. Bas, qachon insonni Robbi sinash uchun ikrom qilsa va ne'mat bersa, \nMeni Robbim ikrom qildi, deydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,107]}]}

{"text":"16. Bas, qachon Robbi sinash \nuchun rizqini tor qilib qo`ysa, \nu: Robbim meni xorladi, deydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,96]}]}

{"text":"21. Yo`q! Vaqtiki, yer zilzilaga tushib, parcha-parcha bo`lib ketsa.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"22. Va Robbing va farishtalar saf-saf bo`lib kelsalar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,54]}]}

{"text":"23. Va o`sha kunda jahannamni keltirsa, o`sha kunda inson eslaydir. Lekin bu eslashdan endi ne foyda.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,101]}]}

{"text":"24. U: Afsuski, oxirat hayotimga ham biror narsa taqdim qilsam bo`lar ekan, deydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,85]}]}

{"text":"25. Bas, o`sha kunda Allohning \nazobiga o`xshash azob-la hech kim azoblamaydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"26. Va Uning bog`lashiga o`xshash hech kim bog`lamaydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"28. Robbingga sen Undan, \nU sendan rozi bo`lgan holda qayt!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"3. Va Volid va undan tarqagan valadlar bilan qasam.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"5. U inson unga hech kimning kuchi yetmas, deb hisoblarmi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,58]}]}

{"text":"17. So`ngra, iymon keltirganlar \nva bir-birini sabrga, mehr-shafqatga chaqirganlar bo`lsa...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,92]}]}
